2017-10-02  Jacek Jendrzej  <satbaby@kawaii.com>

	fix compil after merge

	Merge branch 'master' into pu/mp

2017-10-02  Stefan Seyfried  <seife@tuxbox-git.slipkontur.de>

	helpers/readFile: limit memory allocations

	remove "using namespace std" from header files
	"using namespace std" in headers is considered bad practice, so move it
	either into the respective cpp files or (for files which have lots of
	other std::xxx usage anyway) just write it out explicitly.
	Looking at the headers and the affected cpp files, one can actually see
	why it is bad practice, as it's spreading very far ;-)

2017-09-30  Jacek Jendrzej  <satbaby@kawaii.com>

