2012-10-16  [CST] Focus  <focus.cst@gmail.com>

	driver/record.cpp: use slow record warning option. this warning tested for generic setup with usb hdd and meant to early tell if record buffer usage reach watermark, where user have chance to stop some of records and save others from overflow under high load. if your think you getting false warnings, disable it

	settings: add option to enable/disable slow record warning

	locals: add locale for slow record warning option

